    <authors>Peter Wagner (A.K.A Wagnerp) and Simon Coghlan (A.K.A Smurf-IV), Giduac, Ahmed Abdelhameed, Lesandro, tobitege, Phil Wright (A.K.A ComponentFactory)</authors>
